3. What is the difference between SEO Marketing and SEO Optimization in Saudi Arabia?
SEO Marketing in Saudi Arabia involves promoting products or services through various digital marketing channels, leveraging SEO to drive traffic and conversions. On the other hand, SEO Optimization in Saudi Arabia focuses on refining technical aspects of a website and its content to improve search engine rankings and user experience.
